{"artist": "Nic Klein", "availability": ["arena", "mtgo", "paper"], "boosterTypes": ["draft"], "borderColor": "black", "colorIdentity": [], "colors": [], "convertedManaCost": 3.0, "edhrecRank": 6828, "finishes": ["nonfoil", "foil"], "flavorText": "Knowledge itself is neither good nor evil. Just as the wrong book in the wrong hands could doom all existence, the same book in the right hands could save it.", "foreignData": [{"flavorText": "Wissen an sich ist weder gut noch b\u00f6se. So, wie ein Buch in den falschen H\u00e4nden alles vernichten kann, vermag es in den richtigen H\u00e4nden alles zu retten.", "language": "German", "multiverseId": 447645, "name": "Arkane Enzyklop\u00e4die", "text": "{3}, {T}: Ziehe eine Karte.", "type": "Artefakt"}, {"flavorText": "El conocimiento en s\u00ed no es ni bueno ni malo. Cierto libro en las manos equivocadas podr\u00eda acabar con la existencia, pero el mismo libro en las manos adecuadas podr\u00eda salvarla.", "language": "Spanish", "multiverseId": 447926, "name": "Enciclopedia arcana", "text": "{3}, {T}: Roba una carta.", "type": "Artefacto"}, {"flavorText": "La connaissance n'est en soi ni bonne ni mauvaise. Un mauvais livre entre de mauvaises mains pourrait condamner l'existence, mais le m\u00eame livre entre de bonnes mains pourrait la sauver.", "language": "French", "multiverseId": 448207, "name": "Encyclop\u00e9die \u00e9sot\u00e9rique", "text": "{3}, {T} : Piochez une carte.", "type": "Artefact"}, {"flavorText": "La conoscenza in s\u00e9 non \u00e8 buona n\u00e9 cattiva. Cos\u00ec come il libro sbagliato nelle mani sbagliate potrebbe condannare l'intera esistenza, lo stesso libro nelle mani giuste potrebbe salvarla.", "language": "Italian", "multiverseId": 448488, "name": "Enciclopedia Arcana", "text": "{3}, {T}: Pesca una carta.", "type": "Artefatto"}, {"flavorText": "\u77e5\u8b58\u305d\u306e\u3082\u306e\u306f\u5584\u3067\u3082\u60aa\u3067\u3082\u306a\u3044\u3002\u4e0d\u9069\u5207\u306a\u672c\u304c\u60aa\u610f\u306e\u6